title: We need a powerful logo design for the very first ever Energy School
description:
Hi ! I am looking for a premium logo.
Here is the story behind this logo :
We are launching the first “Energy School” - offering online initiations and courses to learn how to comprehend and harmonize our own energy, how to unlock blocages on the physical, emotional and mental levels in order to unlock a more spiritual dimension to life, to boost vitality and resync with ourselves and life.
The name of the program (and the logo) is “L’École de l’Énergie”.
Why “L’École de l’Énergie” ? It is the French name for “Energy School” and we want to start approaching the concept of energy as a concrete, down to earth matter that has the power to change lives, as everything is energy, yet it remains something a little bit abstract.
Now, to make this school alive, I need an impactful visual identity.
A logo with a high-end perceived value.
The logo in itself will be the two letters : E E - there is potential to create something visually impactful.
However, the full name ““L’École de l’Énergie” has to appear in small under the “E E” monogram logo, as a tagline for exemple, but I am open to proposals.
I need a version of the logo with just the two E's, and one with the full tagline appearing under : L'École de l'Énergie.
It should be the same logo for the two versions.
Energy is fluid, it connects and vibrates. I envision something that screams “connection” and “flow”.
I need a logo that makes people want to come in, connect, share, be part of, expand.
I also have in mind a “mirror” effect of the two E’s that could be interesting. Looking at ourselves and others as mirrors.
An important piece of information is that this program : “L’École de l’Énergie”, is part of our brand : UNISUN.
UNISUN is a movement of re-synchronization with nature and what’s alive. Connecting Humans together. An Integrative and holistic approach to health and life. Our logo UNISUN is attached, and we often use a monogram U that expresses Unity and connection.
Now, how to make our E E logo come alive ?
Here are some ideas to power your creativity :
I like the idea of having a mirroring effect - link between the two E’s :
￼
￼
I like the idea of a visual bond :
￼
Or the expression of flow, with the appearance of an infinity sign through the connecting of the two E’s.
I would like to feel the “movement” aspect in the visual - flying above the ground, fluid and free.
We should feel a touch of magic and curiosity transpiring with the visual.
But it can also be another concept.
Like having a “path” from one E to the other.
Something more abstract or mystical.
But it has to remind high-end and clean/professional looking.
Let your creativity flow !
Just keep in mind that it has to be a premium, impactful logo that catches the eye but reminds simple.
About the colors :
What are the best colors for expressing flow and energy ?
We use a gold yellow as well as a punchy coral in our branding, but we also like the minimalistic approach of a black or white logo. The monogram effect, like a stamp, is important to us.
The color of light, gold, could work too !
Our brand colors references :
coral - #F66A6A
yellow - #FFC600
Thank you in advance and looking forward to seeing proposals soon !
Marine

title: 99NONPROFITS WINNER Homeless Charity 'HOUSE, Inc.' is Looking For a Vintage Style Illustrated Logo
description:
Housing Opportunities to Ultimately Shelter Everyone, Inc (HOUSE, Inc.) was formed in July 2021 for the charitable purpose of providing transitional shared housing for individuals experiencing housing insecurities or who need to live in a drug and alcohol-free environment.
HOUSE, Inc.'s services will:
- Provide recovery assistance and relief for poor and distressed individuals.
- Prevent homelessness and end poverty.
- Improve physical, mental, spiritual, and social well-being.
- Reunite families.
HOUSE, Inc. aims to help individuals who would not qualify for suitable housing for several reasons. Many people we aim to help have a history of mental illness, domestic abuse, or other trauma and a history of addiction or incarceration. HOUSE, Inc.'s shared housing solution gives them another chance to integrate into society as fully functioning citizens.
We will be operating our homes in safe neighborhoods. We look for single-family homes, 3 to 4 bedrooms. It is important that the locations promote a sense of community. A home will ideally not be in a congested city, the home should have enough yard space to allow some privacy and relaxation. Many of our potential residents will be women who have a history of PTSD, depression, anxiety, addiction, and abuse so it is important that they have the impression that we are a group that they can trust and feel safe. This is a second chance for them, and in many cases, these individuals have hit rock bottom. We are here to help them back into a happy and productive life.
Our shared housing model has been used across the US and other countries very successfully. There will be 2 residents per bedroom as having roommates and being social with others in a similar situation helps with recovery. Residents have chores and leadership roles within the house. They hold weekly meetings for governance and for participation in extracurricular activities like yoga or life classes. The principle concept is that residents use each other to help them get through this tough time, but HOUSE, Inc. will provide them all the opportunity to make that happen.
other_notes:
STYLE
I’m interested in vintage-style emblem logos.
KEY VALUES
Trust, safety, caring, giving, professionalism are important values.
IDEAS
- I like the idea of nature being a part of the design.
- I like the small-town feel or suburban-type environment. But not farm, not the city. I'm thinking of a nice home, a tree, and a small yard.
- I like the colors in the images attached but will be open to your ideas.
- I think the full charity name may be too long to include in the design, but if you can do it well, please do.
- I would consider designs with or without a slogan such as:
"Ending Homelessness and Poverty" or "Preventing Homelessness" or "Helping to Prevent Homeless"
Here's our website: houseinc501c3.org

title: We need a creative logo for a new Ketamine Infusion Clinic
description:
Hello,
We are opening a ketamine infusion clinic called Mind Space. What is a ketamine infusion clinic? Ketamine is a psychoactive pharmaceutical drug that has the potential of helping people who suffer from mental illness including chronic pain, depression and anxiety. We are physicians and in our clinic we will give this medication through an IV to patients suffering from these disorders. This is a relatively new and exciting treatment for people who have suffered from mental illness.
Our goal in starting our company is to provide a safe space for people to receive this medication and any potential benefits it has to offer ergo the name of our company - “Mind Space”. This medication is unlike many psychiatric medications in that it does have certain psychedelic properties. Therefore our goal is to not only create a safe physical “space” for our patients in the traditional sense but an elevated mental or metaphysical space for patients. We want our logo to be attention grabbing and would be happy with logos that are abstract.
We want the logo to be primarily used for our website and for any marketing our clinic may do in the future.
other_notes: The design needs to be youthful but also professional. This is a non-traditional medical space that should be reflected in the logo.

title: Design a modern logo for a technology company
description:
VisualCortex is a tech company focused on analysing video data by applying AI technology to both live video streams and video repositories.
At VisualCortex, we have a simple vision. We want to make video the new data frontier for everyone. There is so much valuable information that we observe through videos. Yet, until now, we’ve been letting the data slip by because we’ve lacked the means to easily analyse it and produce actionable insights.
We have designed and developed VisualCortex to enable everyone to capture that value and innovate their new ways of working: From analysing traffic patterns to improve road designs, to analysing foot traffic and dwell times to create more intuitive shopping experiences, or capturing potentially hazardous incidents in order to facilitate safer workplaces.
We believe that making video analytics data highly consumable and easily actionable is a complete game changer.
If possible, include some
Abstract imagery of the company name – ‘VC’ or ‘VisualCortex’
Relevant elements that visually indicate what that company does, such as a brain or video player
We have a preference for simple designs that are clear and concise with high visual acuity.
The design iconography needs to be scalable in various size formats from icon size 64px up to 1024px while maintaining readability and form.
The logo can still be recognised and interpreted clearly in greyscale.
Industry
Technology, Video Intelligence, Analytics, Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence, Computer Vision
other_notes: Open to all ideas and concepts
